<p>Syncplify is a must for companies that want a secure SFTP or FTPS server. It’s one of the most protected offerings on the market. There is an Evaluation version of Syncplify Server, which <strong>has limitations</strong> on its functionality and use – you aren’t allowed to use it for business purposes. Paid versions start at $299 (£229). for an unlimited number of users and concurrent connections. Download <a href="https://www.syncplify.com/download" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-gtm-vis-has-fired1649924_55="1">the free Evaluation version</a>.</p>
